==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Nosel
<hw>Nos"el</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Noursle</er>.]</ety> <def>To nurse; to lead or teach; to foster; to
nuzzle.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>If any man use the Scripture . . . to <qex>nosel</qex> thee in
anything save in Christ, he is a false prophet.</q>
<rj><qau>Tyndale.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Noseless</ent>⟦br⟧
